Package: fairnessToolbox
Type: Package
Title: Modular Fairness Workflow Toolbox
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Maximilian", "Willer", email = "willer.maximilian@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    A modular and extensible framework for fairness-aware machine learning workflows. 
    This package provides interchangeable engines and controllers for preprocessing, 
    training, in-processing, post-processing, evaluation, reporting, and publishing.
    It is designed for flexibility, transparency, and integration with user-defined controls.
